\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 - Validate YAML syntax: http://www.yamllint.com/
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 - Check date format: "2021-11-01" (ISO 8601)
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 **Issue 2: Citation not found**
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 - Check PMID is correct in action.evidenceReferences
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 - Verify citation YAML filename matches: pmid-\{PMID\}.yaml
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 - Check citation is in citationCache
\f1\fs24 \
\

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 **Issue 3: Guideline not linking**
